The paper deals with the use of UAVs for terrain monitoring, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of Gaussian Process models and probabilistic sensors for data fusion and planning, which are common techniques in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the paper also discusses the optimization of trajectories in 3D space, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR).
